➜趁热打铁美股上市！估值超100亿，小鹏汽车是个大肉签吗？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415323478_99994080	21916
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200828/9fa6c6a0870842a4b54cd017eba33604.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/4d8803a65fe64861a7f34af94caafe54.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>本文编辑：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200828/ff1b236a290f443da788fcf89caffd65.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
